flowchart TD
    A[Detection] --> B[Severity Classification]
    B --> C[Assign Incident Commander]
    C --> D[Open War Room]
    D --> E[Assess Business Impact]
    E --> F[Mitigation Plan]
    F --> G[Execute Fix or Rollback]
    G --> H[Validate Recovery]
    H --> I[Communicate Closure]
    I --> J[Post-Incident Review]
    J --> K[Problem Management and Backlog]
